---
import { siteConfig } from "@/config/site.config";
---

<section
  id="contact"
  class="border-t border-slate-800 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-900 to-slate-950"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-20 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-100">
      {siteConfig.cta.title}
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400">
      지금 문의하면 빠르게 제작 방향을 잡아드립니다
    </p>

    <a
      href="mailto:contact@solidweb.kr"
      class="mt-8 inline-flex rounded-xl bg-cyan-500 px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 hover:bg-cyan-400 transition"
    >
      {siteConfig.cta.buttonText}
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
